      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next door neighbor, friend of mine, they knocked on her door too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It seems to me that at that time from what I heard, that see, like I said, they were employing some people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They needed man power.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And who better than the Jew?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All right, Phyllis--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wasn't working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had I been working, maybe I would have remained longer.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
